txt.en: Trolls can be found in the port of Harlond.\n\nYou should defeat Trolls within the port of Harlond.
'Many trolls await orders in the Harlond. You should defeat any trolls in the port if Aragorn and his men are to make landfall with haste.'
Trolls can be found in the port of the Harlond.\n\nYou should defeat trolls within the port of the Harlond.
Aragorn will need the port of the Harlond cleared if he and his men are to make landfall with haste.
